# Dashboard Design Guide

## Pages

1️⃣ Overview Page
- Total Revenue (KPI card)
- Total Orders
- Total Customers
- Date Filter

2️⃣ Monthly Sales Trend
- Line chart of monthly revenue

3️⃣ Top Selling Products
- Bar chart: Product vs Total Sales

4️⃣ Country-wise Sales
- Map visual: Sales by Country

5️⃣ Top Customers
- Table showing customer name, total revenue, number of orders

## Filters

- Date Range
- Country
- Product Category

## Business Impact

- Helps management track overall sales trends
- Identifies top-performing products & regions
- Enables focused sales & marketing strategy
